Q　なぜインドから日本に来て働こうと思った？
Q　ここではどんな仕事をしている？
Q　働いていてどういったやりがいを感じるか？
Q　今後どういった仕事に携わっていきたいか？
 
Q: Why did you decide to come to Japan from India to work?
Q: What kind of work are you doing here?
Q: What kind of fulfillment do you feel from your work?
Q: What kind of work would you like to be involved in going forward?
 
